{"tid":2101709,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"芝拉華特:馬勒當拿贏得的不及美斯1%","createTime":"2020-07-10T04:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T10:20:22.000Z","uid":173952,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b90b865ec73633b26276c9fdf8b0ea3156c6d782","tid":2101709,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:03:18.000Z","msg":"芝拉華特：老馬所贏得的不及美斯1%<br />\n<br />\n  誰才是球壇歷史上最好的球員？對此每個人都有自己的看法。近日巴拉圭名宿芝拉華特（Jose Luis Chilavert）在接受《Cooperativa》電台採訪時表示，美斯（Lionel Messi）就是歷史最佳。<br />\n<br />\n  芝拉華特表示：「美斯就是球壇歷史最佳球員，我喜歡的另外兩名球員是朗拿度（Ronaldo）和羅馬里奧（Romario）。馬勒當拿（Maradona）贏得的東西甚至都不及美斯的百分之一，因此美斯要更加出色。」<br />\n<br />\n報導截圖<br />\n<br />\n  另外在採訪中芝拉華特再次炮轟FIFA主席恩芬天奴（Gianni Infantino），並稱「馬勒當拿仍然是恩芬天奴的擦鞋墊。」"},{"pid":"ae5f0c826dbd1a6bc3bc4f2147d617129d3261ee","tid":2101709,"uid":7199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:38:12.000Z","msg":"老馬真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b16e9e9d87b67a611d7ec8670879a582367fac","tid":2101709,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:58:14.000Z","msg":"馬勒當拿仍然是恩芬天奴的擦鞋墊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d312172bcc6514a3a6185810be1293fe45b3c8","tid":2101709,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T06:05:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9acf8cf627156f32ccba2bf6e59bd48eeb07ec34","tid":2101709,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T06:06:28.000Z","msg":"係咪專射free kick個肥龍門??"},{"pid":"a24b31d8242d5ad8ff8244e76e2f470bf0dcf3d5","tid":2101709,"uid":37297,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T06:08:41.000Z","msg":"淨係計西甲?"},{"pid":"9b394fbd806d3805ba33de314a01f11c8e8e6b56","tid":2101709,"uid":53855,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTim